name: Self Driving Car
description: A vehicle that is capable of sensing its environment and moving safely with little or no human input.

name: Vehicle Traffic Control
description: System that combines traditional traffic lights with an array of sensors and artificial intelligence.

name: Artificial Intelligence
description: Any device that perceives its environment and takes actions that maximize its chance of successfully achieving its goals.

name: Arterial Management
description: Arterial Management strategies are used to effectively and successfully manage traffic and control arterial roadways. Examples are: Traffic signal improvements. Advanced traffic signal control.

name: Collision Avoidance
description: ollision avoidance is the maintenance of systems and practices designed to prevent vehicles (such as aircraft, motor vehicles, ships, and trains) from colliding with each other. Examples include: Airborne collision avoidance systems for aircraft.
